dc_title_s: Landfills, Class III: Prince George's County, Maryland
dc_description_s: Class III landfills accept Municipal Solid Waste (MSW) and is where household garbage is sent to be held and isolated from the surrounding area. This dataset displays the location of permitted or reclaimed Class III fill sites in Prince George's County, Maryland.
dc_creator_sm: Prince George's County Planning Department - Environmental Planning Section, The Maryland-National Capital Park & Planning Commission
